Click the exe folder 
Keep the default location then uncheck the also install support for the graphical user
Click on continue wait till it get 100 % 

Open the system environment for path and give the bin path of the downloaded minnow folder.

Open the cmd and type mingw-get you should get a prompt 
Again on cmd type mingw-get install mingw32-make

It will install make version 3.82 in your system. 



To 
Verify type mingw32-make 

You should get. 

Mingw32-make: ***No target specified and no makefile found. Stop
	

mingw32-make is successfully install in your system which is same as make in linux
